library(tidyverse)
library(Article3Package)

from At reg lines

G.file <- "~/Projects/Data2016_2017/AthalianaGegMapLines/call_method_75/call_method_75_TAIR9.G.rds"
skip_if_not(file.exists(G.file))
s <- FromTrueSampler(G.file = G.file,
                     n = 100,
                     L = 1000,
                     K = 2,
                     prop.outlier = 0.1,
                     rho = 0.9,
                     cs = c(0.5, 0),
                     round = FALSE)
dat <- sampl(s)
# plot
plot(dat)

hist(dat$X)

hist(dat$G)
